### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "userName": "testuser",
  "phone": "+237650123456",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "surName": "User"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yvesdylane24@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Exchange Better Auth session (cookie-based)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/exchange
Cookie: better-auth.session_token=PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### Google token exchange
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "PASTE_BETTER_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Get current user (replace TOKEN with actual JWT from login/Google response)
GET http://localhost:3000/user/me
Authorization: Bearer INSERT_JWT_HERE

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000

### Google test page (open in browser)
# GET http://localhost:3000/auth/test
